The '''Mon Calamari Fish Market''' was a market on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]] during the times of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Galactic Republic]]. A young [[Darth Maul/Legends|Darth Maul]] visited the market briefly upon escaping from the [[Happy Nerf Herder]] home for young boys. While there, he stole a [[Skimboard/Legends|hoverboard]] from a bystander and accidentally caused an explosion which threw him off the building.

